{"tid":1036330,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新婚夫婦抽中3號籌 彭太：入伙後馬上準備生B (圖)","createTime":"2019-02-25T07:05:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-25T07:46:23.000Z","uid":72009,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"27a4fd8cd3ae5c2218b14aee4b6d5a7a7578e907","tid":1036330,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T07:05:06.000Z","msg":"以市價42折推售的綠置居項目長沙灣麗翠苑今日攪珠，有申請人特地到現場觀看攪珠結果。<br />\n  在場一對居大圍公屋的彭姓夫婦抽中69號第3粒珠，感到非常興奮。兩人於去年結婚，今次是首次申請資助房屋，心儀兩房一廳單位。彭先生對結果感興奮，其妻更以「發緊夢」來形容兩人的幸運，並聲言入伙後會馬上準備生育。<br />\n  房委會資助房屋小組委員會主席黃遠輝在攪珠後表示，麗翠苑共提供2545個單位，估計攪出的首6個號碼申請人有機會揀樓。早上攪珠攪出的首10個號碼順序為：48、58、69、21、29、80、46、02、89、49。第11至20個號碼順序為：95、70、18、38、34、91、68、12、76、42。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/NxYVQ1DEHZTJH9bLOecU.g--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20190225a134435.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FNxYVQ1DEHZTJH9bLOecU.g--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20190225a134435.jpg&h=088df3f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n看完圖建議現在準備定"},{"pid":"d32c5cddf014fb4a6046452a33d20f1de6583295","tid":1036330,"uid":40470,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T07:13:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同我扯"},{"pid":"b8766428ea862e3eaafcc66e1d5f05804359edcd","tid":1036330,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d32c5cddf014fb4a6046452a33d20f1de6583295","tid":1036330,"uid":40470,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T07:13:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同我扯"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T07:15:15.000Z","msg":"彭太應該70後 , 有錯勿怪"},{"pid":"2b7bae97646d52206867186e64759cd670ea56b8","tid":1036330,"uid":107927,"like":0,"dislike":1,"s